tecture.md:92:A predefined strategy (§STRAT-forge-predefined-strategy-contract) is the named\\n./forge/docs/workflows/architecture.md:105:(§STRAT-forge-predefined-strategy-contract).\\n./forge/docs/workflows/dynamic-access.md:26:All three engines are selected by predefined strategy bundles. The strategy\\n./forge/docs/workflows/dynamic-access.md:30:(§STRAT-forge-predefined-strategy-contract).\\n./forge/docs/workflows/add-new-library-support.md:35:basic iterative strategy bundles (§STRAT-predefined-strategy-parameter-families),\\n./forge/README.md:79:§STRAT-forge-predefined-strategy-contract\\n./forge/README.md:110:Strategies are declared in `strategies/predefined_strategies.json`. Prompt text\\n./forge/prompt_templates/persistent/default_agent_rules.md:6:- Never generate, write, or modify reachability metadata or Native Image config entries. Do not create or edit `reachability-metadata.json`, `reflect-config.json`, `resource-config.json`, `proxy-config.json`, `serialization-config.json`, `jni-config.json`, `predefined-classes-config.json`, or any other file under `src/test/resources/META-INF/native-image`; Forge handles metadata generation and merging externally.\\n./forge/prompt_templates/persistent/dynamic_access_rules.md:20:- Never generate, write, or modify reachability metadata or Native Image config entries. Do not create or edit `reachability-metadata.json`, `reflect-config.json`, `resource-config.json`, `proxy-config.json`, `serialization-config.json`, `jni-config.json`, `predefined-classes-config.json`, or any other file under `src/test/resources/META-INF/native-image`; Forge handles metadata generation and merging externally.\\n./forge/DEVELOPING.md:80:- `--strategy-name NAME` select a predefined workflow strategy from `strategies/predefined_strategies.json`. Defaults to `javac_iterative_with_coverage_sources_pi_gpt-5.5`.\\n./forge/DEVELOPING.md:125:- `--strategy-name NAME` select a predefined workflow strategy from `strategies/predefined_strategies.json`. Defaults to `basic_iterative_pi_gpt-5.4` (Pi agent).\\n./forge/DEVELOPING.md:227:- Run `ai_workflows/drivers/add_new_library_support.py` for a predefined set of libraries.\\n./forge/DEVELOPING.md:235:  - `strategy`: strategy name matching an entry in `strategies/predefined_strategies.json`.\\n./forge/DEVELOPING.md:271:Agents are registered via `Agent.register(...)` and selected per-strategy through the `agent` field in `strategies/predefined_strategies.json`; see [docs/agent.md](docs/agent.md) for the agent API and Pi adapter architecture. Supported agents:\\n./forge/DEVELOPING.md:330:    python3 utility_scripts/schema_validator.py strategy strategies/predefined_strategies.json\\n./forge/DEVELOPING.md:347:The project uses registry-based workflow and agent abstractions. Each workflow strategy is a Python class that inherits from `WorkflowStrategy` and is registered via a decorator. Agents are registered in the same way via `Agent.register(...)`. Strategies are configured through `strategies/predefined_strategies.json`, which defines the workflow, agent, model, optional provider, prompts, optional persistent instructions, and parameters for each strategy.\\n./forge/DEVELOPING.md:353:If you want to run an existing workflow with a different model or tuned parameters, add a new entry to `strategies/predefined_strategies.json`. Reuse the same `workflow` and `agent` as the base strategy, and differentiate by appending a space and a descriptor to the name:\\n./forge/DEVELOPING.md:393:1. **Add a strategy entry** to `strategies/predefined_strategies.json` with the matching workflow, agent, prompts, and parameters.\\n./forge/DEVELOPING.md:427:Dynamic-access strategies can optionally download library source code, upstream tests, and/or documentation as read-only agent context. This is configured per strategy via the `source-context-types` parameter in `predefined_strategies.json`. Available types are `main`, `test`, and `documentation`. The artifacts are downloaded from URLs in the library's `index.json` (populated by the `populateArtifactURLs` Gradle task) and extracted to `local_repositories/source_context/<group>/<artifact>/<version>/`.\\n./forge/DEVELOPING.md:431:Multiple predefined strategies exist in `strategies/predefined_strategies.json`, each using a different source-context combination:\\n./forge/AGENTS.md:35:- If the change only alters wording or agent instructions, prefer `prompt_templates/` or `strategies/predefined_strategies.json` over Python logic.\\n./forge/AGENTS.md:46:- `strategies/predefined_strategies.json`: declarative workflow configuration such as strategy names, prompt files, parameters, model, and agent selection. §STRAT-workflow-strategy-registry\\n./docs/functional-spec.md:272:- For Forge: a predefined strategy name selecting workflow engine, agent,\\n\",\"exit_code\":0,\"status\":\"completed\"}}\n{\"type\":\"item.started\",\"item\":{\"id\":\"item_57\",\"type\":\"command_execution\",\"command\":\"/usr/bin/bash -lc 'export GRAALVM_HOME=/home/vjovanov/c/graalvm-reachability-metadata/vj/forge/ce/sdk/latest_graalvm_home JAVA_HOME=/home/vjovanov/c/graalvm-reachability-metadata/vj/forge/ce/sdk/latest_graalvm_home PATH=\\\"$GRAALVM_HOME/bin:$PATH\\\"; native-image --expert-options-all | rg -n '\\\"'predefined|class data|class-data|AOTClassRegistry'\\\"\",\"aggregated_output\":\"\",\"exit_code\":null,\"status\":\"in_progress\"}}\n{\"type\":\"item.completed\",\"item\":{\"id\":\"item_57\",\"type\":\"command_execution\",\"command\":\"/usr/bin/bash -lc 'export GRAALVM_HOME=/home/vjovanov/c/graalvm-reachability-metadata/vj/forge/ce/sdk/latest_graalvm_home JAVA_HOME=/home/vjovanov/c/graalvm-reachability-metadata/vj/forge/ce/sdk/latest_graalvm_home PATH=\\\"$GRAALVM_HOME/bin:$PATH\\\"; native-image --expert-options-all | rg -n '\\\"'predefined|class data|class-data|AOTClassRegistry'\\\"\",\"aggregated_output\":\"1154:                                               Files describing predefined classes that can be loaded at runt